    <Apparatus>
        <Critical/>
        <Commentary>
            <ab>Y3.3c <em>gąm jīuuiiąm āiiese yešti</em>] add. ante <em>gą̇m baoiriią̇m āiie(se)
                    yešti</em> 235, 672, 677, 4370. Vid. <em>baoiriia-</em>
                <bibl>Bartholomae, 1904</bibl> "chewable" (the edible part of the cow, i.e. "the
                meat") vs. <em>gąm jīuuiiąm</em> "the living cow" referring to the "milk". For solid offerings to the waters s. N49.22-23</ab>
        </Commentary>
    </Apparatus>
    <Parallels>
        <ab>Y3.3 ≈ Y7.4, DrYt1.2; ~ Y22.2 + Y22.3, Y22.22 + Y22.23, Y22.25, Y24.6 + Y24.7, Y25.1 +
            Y25.2</ab>
        <ab>
            <em>aiβiiō vaŋᵛhībiiō [...] āpəm haōmiiąm</em> ~ VrS27.4, VrS27.10 <em>aiβiiō vaŋᵛhībiiō
                apəmca haōmiiąm</em></ab>
            <ab>
                <em>aiβiiō vaŋᵛhībiiō</em> = Y1.13, Y2.13, Y3.3, Y3.15, Y4.18, Y6.12, Y7.16, 17.12,
                Y22.16, Y24.23, Y59.12, Y66.13, VrS78.25, VrS79.18, VrS81.12, VrS82.13, VS12.2,
                VS12.4, VS12.6, VS12.8, VS12.10, VS12.12, VS12.14, VS12.14, VS12.16, VS12.18,
                VS12.20, VS14.4, VS18.70, VS18.72; ~ Yt5 <em>passim</em>
                <em>vaŋᵛhi səuuište arəduuī sūre anāhite</em>
            </ab>
            <ab><em>apəm haōmiiąm</em> = VrS27.2, VrS27.8.</ab>
            <ab><em>gąm jīuuiiąm āiiese yešti uruuarąm haδānaēpatąm aṣ̌aiia uzdātąm</em> ~ VrS27.3, VrS27.9 <em>imąmca gąm jīuuiiąm aṣ̌aiia uzdātąm imąmca uruuarąm haδānaēpatąm aṣ̌aiia uzdātąm</em>
        </ab>
            <ab><em>uruuarąm haδānaēpatąm</em> ~ Y62.9 ~ <em>uruuarąm vā haδānaēpatąm</em>.</ab>
    </Parallels>
